## GitHub Pages Cache Headers
## Ensure templates are never aggressively cached so deployments reflect immediately.
## For template JS files: short/no cache so updates propagate fast.
## For static assets like style.css: longer cache is fine.

/script.js
  Cache-Control: no-cache, no-store, must-revalidate
  Pragma: no-cache

/templates/*
  Cache-Control: no-cache, no-store, must-revalidate
  Pragma: no-cache

/style.css
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=86400

/*.html
  Cache-Control: no-cache, no-store, must-revalidate
  Pragma: no-cache
